title: Parmesan-Crumbed Chicken Schnitzel with Pear, Toasted Almonds & Parmesan Salad
description: It's easy to whip up a classic schnitzel at home, and we're going to show you how! Then, make it a meal with a
sweet and savoury salad, studded with pear and almonds, plus some garlic aioli for dipping. Delicious!

